    "If however, we increase σ µ = 2 (leaving all other parameters as specified), we still haveR σ 0 (0, b δ) ≈ 0.971, but now 4 = β δ 2 σ 2 µ > δ = 0.2.Thus according to theorem 4.4, the infections should still exhibit exponential decay, but we can no longer guarantee stability for the DFE.",
